						               													<description>The deluxe version of the hilarious headline card game! Players compete to create attention grabbing and often crazy headlines. This version includes a game board, dry-erase marker, and rewriteable cards. Who will earn the most points and earn the biggest laughs. To start shuffle the red cards and put the pile face down next to the board. Each player is dealt a hand of 5 blue cards with words on them, each with a point value. At the beginning of a round turn over the top three red cards and place them on the corresponding spaces on the board. When it's your turn, a player may dicard up to 3 cards form their hand and replace them with cards from the blue deck. The goal is to construct a headline using the cards in your hand and up to 2 of the face up red cards from the board. Cards played earn the printed point value on the card and are played to the 7 headline spots on the board. If you can not make a headline you must pass and may discard and replace any number of cards. At the end of your turn add up the value of the played cards and move your scoring token. The first player to get to 500 points wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The deluxe version adds 3 new types of Exclusive cards which can give your story a boost and add extra points or options.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
